// WELCOME Come back Guide/Contact Welcome to ReCrea! In ReCrea, we are committed to the idea that something that is no longer useful for some can become a treasure for others. Our mission is to give a second life to those old or broken electronic devices that often end up in a forgotten corner. We want you to see the potential in what you no longer use and, together, we will transform those devices into jewels of all kinds.\n\n The magic of ReCrea lies in the collaboration of generous people and companies who wish to donate their old electronic devices for a charitable cause. In partnership with the Virgen De Gracia center in Puertollano and other non-profit organizations, we channel our efforts to raise funds and bring help to those who need it most.\n\n Here, we are all agents of change. Whether you have an old phone, a computer that no longer turns on, or any other device that you think is no longer useful, ReCrea offers you a platform where you can donate and make a difference.\n\n Every donation counts. Every small gesture of generosity becomes an opportunity to improve lives and communities. So join us, discover the potential in what you no longer use, and help make the world a better place.\n\n Thank you for being part of ReCrea. Together, we can turn old technology into smiles and hope. Welcome to a community of positive change!
